|CKBPocket Sand: Tactical Geology|000

Syntax: pocketsand [foe]

At Rank 4 and Contraband 2, fling a handful of allegedly tactical grit at a
nearby foe. Dexterity, Charisma, and Contraband improve the chance to blind.
The attempt begins combat, and you will need a moment to find another
pocketful afterward.
